{"tid":2111871,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"Johnnie Walker 宣佈將在 2021 年發售紙瓶包裝威士忌","createTime":"2020-07-17T01:17:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T17:53:41.000Z","uid":52215,"like":7,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"4bfd1665e40765030cb04d979d235ad2d02f7836","tid":2111871,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:17:44.000Z","msg":"Johnnie Walker 宣佈將在 2021 年發售紙瓶包裝威士忌<br />\n<br />\n威士忌大廠 Johnnie Walker 早先正式宣佈，旗下所有蘇格蘭威士忌在 2021 年都將以紙瓶包裝取代傳統玻璃瓶，此環保決策為母公司 Diageo 減少碳排放計畫的其中一環，該可回收且零塑料的紙瓶由永續採購木材製成，為 Diageo 與風險管理公司 Pilot Lite 合作開發，同時雙方還成立了一間永續包裝技術公司 Pulpex Limited，繼續專注於開發各項產品的包裝紙瓶，目前 Unilever 和 PepsiCo 皆是其合作客戶。而 Diageo 其實也並非首間運用環保紙瓶的公司，Coca-Cola、Absolut 及 L&rsquo;Oreal 等企業都對此持續投入，相信未來隨著聯合國目標與各國法規的規範，對地球無益的非永續包裝都將逐漸被替代。"},{"pid":"c004d50fb4c158994fb639140dce1d2565ea36c8","tid":2111871,"uid":111253,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:19:30.000Z","msg":"戇鳩架?"},{"pid":"bb53dc2c346eda8b55c2cb186768762be65f26a9","tid":2111871,"uid":52215,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:21:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w9r88WN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw9r88WN.jpg&h=5128c104&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"251ce651c0a068a49c756d02ae4cbaf6d70cdfce","tid":2111871,"uid":41411,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:24:18.000Z","msg":"ON9 咁whisky唔好放入木桶呀笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />木桶都要靠斬樹"},{"pid":"ccfab8a7b74fbff811ea0ea748e7296eea9d1b89","tid":2111871,"uid":32934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:25:57.000Z","msg":"898"},{"pid":"a4b68ef52e1126e922aac90062acf4074ade1515","tid":2111871,"uid":104585,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:26:22.000Z","msg":"環保d有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg